INSTALLATION
Jast copy folder with plugin to rutorrent/plugins

CONFIG
As it only beta auto detect of mobile device turned off. To enable it edit 'init.js' file. In first line change 'plugin.enableAutodetect = false;' to 'plugin.enableAutodetect = true;'.

USING
If you enabled autodetect plugin will automaticaly load when detecting mobile device. Another way is adding '?mobile=1' to url of rutorrent.